{"word":"Beard","slug":"beard","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Beard</b> Worn long by:<br/> - Aaron<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=133&verse=2'>Psa 133:2</a> <br/> - Samson<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=16&verse=17'>Jdg 16:17</a> <br/> - David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=21&verse=13'>1Sa 21:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=5&verse=1'>Eze 5:1</a> <br/> Shaven by Egyptians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=14'>Gen 41:14</a><br/> Untrimmed in mourning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=19&verse=24'>2Sa 19:24</a><br/> Plucked<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=9&verse=3'>Ezr 9:3</a><br/> Cut<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=7&verse=20'>Isa 7:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=15&verse=2'>Isa 15:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=41&verse=5'>Jer 41:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=48&verse=37'>Jer 48:37</a><br/> Lepers required to shave<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=13&verse=33'>Lev 13:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=14&verse=9'>Lev 14:9</a><br/> Idolatrous practice of marring, forbidden<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=19&verse=27'>Lev 19:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=21&verse=5'>Lev 21:5</a><br/> Beards of David's ambassadors half shaven by the king of the Amorites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=10&verse=4'>2Sa 10:4</a>"}]}